cs.CV, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper focuses on optimizing queries of spatiotemporal information of objects in video using neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also introduces a declarative extension of SQL for video analytics, which relates to database systems (cs.DB). The optimization techniques presented in the paper involve using NNs as control variates and a novel search algorithm, which are both related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
